name: R B
text: Pizza hut SELLS their customer information. Don't believe me? You can find it on their website. They don't even tell you up front! You have to opt out after the fact! Unless you want you information sold to random third parties, DON'T DO ANY BUSINESS WITH THIS COMPANY!
